  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Single dose tranexamic acid (TA) before dacryocystorhinostomy (DCR) operation: a prospective,
      double blind, placebo controlled study.

      The study hypothesis: TA in DCR might reduce the intraoperative and postoperative bleeding in
      DCR surgery, and might reduce the duration of the surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
