  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  obstruction of nasolacrimal pathway

          -  eligible for DCR surgery

          -  18 years of age or older

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  warfarin treatment

          -  renal insufficiency

          -  pregnancy

          -  mental retardation

          -  tendency to bleed

          -  thromboembolic disease

          -  thrombophilia
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
